high_descs: Turn 180 degrees, move towards and face the covered area of sink.
Pick up the knife left of the tomato.
Slice the tomato next to the sink.
Turn right, move forward a bit and face the area of the sink with the drain in view.
Place the knife in the sink.
Turn left, move forward a bit and then face the covered area of the sink.
Pick up one tomato slice from the area next to the open sink.
Turn right, move towards the green recycling bin, then turn right and move towards and face the microwave.

Open the microwave and place the tomato slice on the plate next to the apple. Close the microwave and turn it on. Open the microwave and remove the cooked tomato slice from the plate. Close the microwave.
Turn right and move towards the stool. Turn right after the stool and face the sink.
Place the cooked tomato slice into the sink next to the left of the knife.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooked tomato slice into the sink.

high_descs: turn around and approach the kitchen sink ahead
grab the knife off of the left side kitchen sink
cut up the red pepper on the left side of the sink
move to the right a bit to face the right side of the kitchen sink
place the knife inside of the right side kitchen sink
move to the left a bit to face the left side of the kitchen sink
grab a piece of the red pepper
turn around and walk to the microwave to the right of the fridge in the left corner of the room
place the red pepper inside of the microwave, microwave it, then take it back out
turn around and walk back over to the sink on the opposite side of the room
place the red pepper inside the right side sink
anns.task_desc: place a microwaved red pepper slice inside the sink

high_descs: Move across the room to the counter by the sink.
Pick up the knife that is on the counter.
Slice the tomato that is on the backside of the counter.
Move back to the sink.
Put the knife in the sink.
Move back to the slice tomato.
Pick up a slice of tomato off the counter.
Move across the room to the microwave. Open the door.
Put the tomato inside the microwave and heat it.  Open he door and pick up the tomato.
Close the door.  Move across the room to the sink.
Put the tomato in the sink.
